description.content:
Available for new orders!

 

Looking for a dedicated and expert web developer? You're in the right place!

 

With over 10 years of experience in custom web development, I specialize in PHP, Laravel, CodeIgniter, ReactJs, and VueJs. From building custom websites to fixing bugs and optimizing performance, I've got you covered.

 

Here are the services offered in this gig:


  • PHP Development
  • Laravel Development
  • CodeIgniter Development
  • SQL / MongoDB Database Management
  • SAAS (Software as a Service) Solutions
  • Full Web Development from Scratch
  • Adding New Features to Existing Projects
  • Bug Fixing and Troubleshooting
  • Upgrading to the Latest Software Versions
  • Seamless Payment Gateway Integration (PayPal, Stripe, and more)
  • Website Speed Optimization
  • On-page SEO Optimization
  • Codecanyon Scripts setup and customization
  • Ongoing site maintenance & support 
  • and many more..


Let's bring your web development vision to life

 

contact me now and let's get started on creating a powerful and stunning website tailored to your specific needs!


Regards


Rashid Ashraf

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why choose custom website development over templates or pre-built websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Custom development allows us to create a website that is fully personalized to your needs. It ensures a unique design, specific features, and enhanced functionality that aligns perfectly with your business goals.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to develop a custom website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The timeline can vary based on the complexity of your project. Generally, custom website development takes several weeks to a few months to ensure high-quality results.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you work with my existing website and improve it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Certainly! We can assess your current website, identify areas for improvement, and implement changes to enhance its performance, design, and user experience.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer responsive design for mobile devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! All the websites we develop are fully responsive, providing an optimal viewing experience on various devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, as part of the custom website development process, we prioritize search engine optimization (SEO) best practices to improve your website's visibility and ranking on search engines.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I request additional features and changes during the development process?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course! We encourage open communication, and you can request additional features or modifications throughout the development process to ensure your website meets your expectations.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What technologies do you use for custom website development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We are proficient in using a wide range of technologies, including PHP, JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3, and various modern frameworks like Laravel, CodeIgniter, ReactJs, and VueJs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do I get started with custom website development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To get started, simply reach out to us via the contact information provided in our gig. We will initiate a discussion about your project requirements and how we can best assist you in bringing your vision to life!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you provide examples of websites you have previously developed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Certainly! I can showcase my portfolio of past projects that highlight our expertise in diverse industries and demonstrate the range of solutions I've delivered to satisfied clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you ensure the security of my custom website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Security is paramount to me. I employ industry-standard security protocols and practices to safeguard your website from potential threats and vulnerabilities.
